Project Title:  Customer Conversion Funnel Analysis
Tools Used: MySQL

1.Funnel Stage Count (Drop-off Analysis)
SELECT 
    Event,
    COUNT(*) AS total_users
FROM funnel_data
GROUP BY Event
ORDER BY FIELD(Event, 'Browser', 'Product View', 'Add to Cart', 'Checkout', 'Purchase');
